sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C as クライアント
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant T as Transfer Service
    participant R as Redis (冪等/制限)
    participant U as User Directory
    participant F as Fraud Engine
    participant A as Account/Ledger Service
    participant DB as Ledger DB (Aurora)
    participant MQ as Event Bus (Kafka)
    participant N as Notification

    C->>GW: POST /transfers (Idempotency-Key, JWT)
    GW->>GW: JWT検証 / レート制限
    GW->>T: createTransfer(req)

    T->>R: SETNX idem:{key} = PROCESSING
    alt キー既存 (重複リクエスト)
        R-->>T: 既存の結果を返却
        T-->>C: 200 (前回と同一レスポンス)
    else 新規リクエスト
        R-->>T: OK (ロック取得)
        T->>U: resolve(email/phone) → recipientId
        T->>R: 日次/取引限度チェック ($500 / $2,500)
        T->>F: 不正ルール評価 (同期)
        alt 高リスク
            F-->>T: REVIEW/DENY
            T-->>C: 422 (要レビュー)
        else 許可
            F-->>T: ALLOW
            T->>A: executeTransfer(from,to,amount,txnId)
            A->>DB: BEGIN (SERIALIZABLE)
            A->>DB: 残高チェック + 二重仕訳 (debit/credit)
            A->>DB: ledger_entries に追記 (immutable)
            A->>DB: COMMIT
            DB-->>A: OK
            A-->>T: SUCCESS
            T->>R: SET idem:{key} = SUCCESS(result)
            T->>MQ: publish TransferCompleted
            T-->>C: 201 Created (txnId, status=COMPLETED)
            MQ-->>N: 受取人へ通知 (Push/SMS)
            MQ-->>A: (履歴サービスへ非同期反映)
        end
    end
